item.dc:creator: @OWNER_2007 OWNER 2007
item.description:
@OWNER_2007 wrote:

Open up your server source file, find runserver, right click that and click on edit.
Now replace everything that it has in it to this,

@echo off title Runserver set java="C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\java.exe" java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server pause
Click on file, save, exit and double click runserver. Hope i helped :D
